data.description: Perfectly located 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms single story home for sale that welcomes you with a large paved driveway. Walk into a large living/dining combination before you get to an open layout kitchen and a bright family room that leads into a large background perfect to enjoy Miami's year round summer. Property features tile flooring, washer and dryer and is fenced for privacy. Note: this is a probate sale long closing maybe needed.
